{"tid":1432443,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"在直播見到藍色商戶：西環張記口水雞","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:41:02.000Z","uid":67292,"like":190,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c57d86d768f68c302ab4b6b97a5883a90143e5","tid":1432443,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"話說剛才我睇Now既民間記者會直播，見到有人留言話：「講大話，露臉喇！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qEdGCs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qEdGCs.jpg&h=71cd4a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我見佢咁型，自己又無頭像，就禁入去睇下，點知原來是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">「張記口水雞」</span></span>老細，真係失敬失敬。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100008104932989&amp;__tn__=%2Cd*F*F-R&amp;eid=ARDn6ReuU8spr4BlwGYficNi4fqVhMcQAQNcYxDyBH-RwKlCnT3q1TZXaDffb_L-bMRTrvrK4Z6p0u3P&amp;tn-str=*F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fid%3D100008104932989%26__tn__%3D%252Cd%2AF%2AF-R%26eid%3DARDn6ReuU8spr4BlwGYficNi4fqVhMcQAQNcYxDyBH-RwKlCnT3q1TZXaDffb_L-bMRTrvrK4Z6p0u3P%26tn-str%3D%2AF&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7xVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=64ddda30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100008104932989&amp;__tn__=%2Cd*F*F-R&amp;eid=ARDn6ReuU8spr4BlwGYficNi4fqVhMcQAQNcYxDyBH-RwKlCnT3q1TZXaDffb_L-bMRTrvrK4Z6p0u3P&amp;tn-str=*F</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FEAXoRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFEAXoRz.jpg&h=6404568c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附上有關留言圖片同連結，等西區同港大巴絲判斷一下，以後仲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫唔幫襯</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOpenrice連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E5%BC%B5%E8%A8%98%E5%8F%A3